channel.title: Where do I put commands?
channel.description:
Ummm... I'm kinda new at coding and was wondering, do I have to put commands in a certain spot. How do I know if a command works or not? Why when I add a command and compile it gives me 100 errors?!?
LOL Thanks

item.title: Where do I put commands?
item.dc:creator: @games-for-pros games-for-pros
item.description:
@games-for-pros wrote:

ok, if u get 100 errors then u pretty much need to start over, and to put commands open your client.java and search for:

if(command.startsWith

youll see a whole command list, just put anywhere there, after 1st one or whatever
